headline: Albertsons® Companies Launches "for U™ Travel," a New Travel Booking Experience Rewarding Customers with Cashback on Flights, Hotels and More
summary: BOISE, Idaho, September 23, 2025--Albertsons Companies, Inc. (NYSE: ACI) today announced the launch of for U Travel, a new travel booking experience that rewards customers with meaningful cashback on both air and non-air travel. Powered by Expedia®, for U Travel allows customers to plan their next getaway directly through the Albertsons Cos. banner for U™ app or website, turning everyday loyalty into unforgettable journeys.

headline: Albertsons links grocery savings with travel bookings
summary: The grocer added a feature to its loyalty program that lets people earn cash back when they arrange airfare, hotel stays, car rentals and vacation packages.
